snippet.title: 2010 AQHA Mare- Phenominal breeding and Deposition!
snippet.description:
2010 AQHA Mare
Wana Kiss N Tell "Chanel"
Breeding includes Skippa Star and Invester. Add her to be apart of your breeding program. 
I am 2nd owner, previously owned by a trainer
Shown 4h and open by a 17 year old as a 2y.o. at local county fair. Chanel is always in the ribbons.
Has been ridden around barking dogs, bucking horses, full team of draft horses, in a grass field alone away from the heard, next to misbehaving kids on the rail at a show, loud gun shots and fireworks, tractors and trucks, would excel as trail horse.
This mare is lightly started Walk/ Trot. Will be a showmanship machine with a little polishing. Already has a great foundation. 
UTD on shoeing, shots and worming, has 2013 coggins
Only reason for sale is owner is upgrading and switching to PBHA. Call for more information. Megan- (262) 902-1720. 
$1,100 OBO
Additional pictures and info available on request!
